            <h1 style="color:#2a63be;">Fitness Criteria</h1>
        </center>
        
        
        <h4 style="color:#2a63be;">
            Persons suffering from following are unfit to drive:
        </h4>
        <p style="color:#2a63be;">
            1. Defects of vision which cannot be corrected by spectacles.<br />
            2. Color or Night Blindness.<br />
            3. Hearing defects which cannot be corrected with the help of hearing aid.<br />
            4. Epilepsy. <br />
            5. Sudden attacks of loss of consciousness or giddiness. <br />
            6. Who has lost either hand or foot. <br />
            7. Suffer from any other disease or disability likely to cause danger to other road users while driving.
            <br />
            <br />
        </p>
        
        
